results.text: Mr. Speaker, due to the birth of my first child I was unable to be present for votes taken May 18 through 19, 22, and 24 through 25, as well as for some votes on May 23. Had I been present, I would have voted as follows: Roll Call Vote Number 263 (Previous Question on H. Res. 324): NO. Roll Call Vote Number 264 (Passage of H. Res. 324): NO.
